l 'Fukushima's Sukagawa Hosts Taimatsu Akashi with Nationwide Material Support'] (Asahi.com, November 12, 2011)</ref><ref>[http://www.yomiuri.co.jp/national/news/20111113-OYT1T00264.htm 'Flames of Recovery Brighten Fukushima - Taimatsu Akashi Held'] (Yomiuri Online, November 13, 2011)</ref> * The {{ill|2020|ja|2020th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and {{ill|2021|ja|2021st year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} festivals were held without spectators to prevent the spread of COVID-19.
