== Access == * Sukagawa City is about 1 hour from {{ill|Tokyo|ja|東京|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokyo|qq=}} via the [[:en:Tōhoku Shinkansen|Tōhoku Shinkansen]] (transfer at [[:en:Kōriyama Station|Koriyama Station (Fukushima)]]), and approximately 1 hour 40 minutes from {{ill|Sendai|ja|仙台|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sendai|qq=}} or [[:en:Utsunomiya|Utsunomiya]]. * 15-minute walk from [[:en:Sukagawa Station|Sukagawa Station]] (JR Line). * 5-minute drive from {{ill|Sukagawa Interchange|ja|須賀川インターチェンジ|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sukagawa Interchange|qq=}} on the [[:en:Tōhoku Expressway|Tōhoku Expressway]]. * Approximately 2,000 parking spaces are available near the venue.
